Nostalgic - 90s.analysis: New Radicals, Toad the Wet Sprocket, Sublime, RHCP 'Aeroplane', Foo Fighters. Specific decade longing. Alt-rock memories. MTV generation. Grunge and optimism.
Nostalgic - 90s.proximity_notes: Near Nostalgic center with Happy pull. 90s = specific era memory, upbeat nostalgia.

Nostalgic - 2000s.analysis: Manic Street Preachers, The Script, Foo Fighters, Sugarcult. Y2K memories. Pop-punk and post-grunge. Coming of age in new millennium.
Nostalgic - 2000s.proximity_notes: Near Nostalgic center between Happy and Sad. 2000s = recent era nostalgia, bittersweet.

Nostalgic - Simpler Times.analysis: Beastie Boys 'Sabotage', Genesis, Aphex Twin, Chemical Brothers, Primus. Longing for less complexity. When life felt easier. Wishing to go back.
Nostalgic - Simpler Times.proximity_notes: Between Nostalgic and Sad/Peaceful. Simpler times = yearning nostalgia, loss of innocence.

Angry - Rage.analysis: Fit for an Autopsy, The Acacia Strain, deathcore intensity. Pure fury. Uncontrolled anger. Screaming energy. Maximum aggression.
Angry - Rage.proximity_notes: Very close to Angry center. Rage = pure concentrated anger at peak intensity.

Angry - Frustrated.analysis: Pearl Jam 'Black', Derek and the Dominos 'Layla', Type O Negative. Blocked and stuck. Helpless anger. Things not working. Irritation with sadness.
Angry - Frustrated.proximity_notes: Between Angry and Sad/Anxious. Frustration = anger + helplessness + worry.

Angry - Aggressive.analysis: Methwitch, Brand of Sacrifice, Terrorizer, Napalm Death. Outward hostility. Attack mode. Confrontational. Physical anger energy.
Angry - Aggressive.proximity_notes: Very close to Angry center with Energy. Aggressive = focused directed anger, combative.

Angry - Cathartic Anger.analysis: Pink Floyd 'Wish You Were Here', Genesis 'No Reply At All', Aphrodite's Child. Releasing anger healthily. Processing through rage. Therapeutic fury.
Angry - Cathartic Anger.proximity_notes: Between Angry and Sad/Introspective. Cathartic = anger as release, healing rage.

Bitter - Resentful.analysis: MEGA DRIVE, Pendulum, The Divine Comedy. Holding grudges. Can't let go. Simmering negativity. Poisoned by past wrongs.
Bitter - Resentful.proximity_notes: Near Bitter center between Angry and Sad. Resentful = bitter + lingering anger + hurt.

Bitter - Betrayed.analysis: Babes in Toyland 'Bruise Violet', Rollins Band 'Liar', Silverstein. Feeling wronged. Trust broken. Wounded and vengeful. Specific hurt.
Bitter - Betrayed.proximity_notes: Between Bitter and Angry/Sad. Betrayed = bitterness from specific violation, trust destroyed.

Excited - Adventure.analysis: Two Steps From Hell, Thomas Bergersen epic scores. Quest and exploration. Unknown territory. Bold discovery. Thrilling anticipation.
Excited - Adventure.proximity_notes: Near Excited center pulled toward Happy/Energy. Adventure = excited exploration, bold joy.
